posts.post_title: ** T216 SCRAP BLANK BACK / PROOF ** Wiltse w/ Oversized Borders for Sale...SOLD!!
posts.post_content:
Another insane printing freak / oddity, this time from the t216 set.  This is a handcut card with about the worst cutting job that ever could have existed on a card, but the Wiltse did come out of this with insanely oversized borders. 

Also features a blank back and what looks like a "hashmark" of some sorts on the left border indicating it could even be a Proof.

Asking $800 for one or the most severe Scrap / Proof cards to come out of my collection!

Thanks!
Brian
